Package org.opends.guitools.controlpanel.browser

Class NodeRefresher

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.guitools.controlpanel.browser.AbstractNodeTask
      • org.opends.guitools.controlpanel.browser.NodeRefresher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable
    public class NodeRefresher
extends AbstractNodeTask
    The class that is in charge of doing the LDAP searches required to update a node: search the local entry, detect if it has children, retrieve the attributes required to render the node, etc.
